t, 得個講字嫁咋, 上頭比壓力, 班大官咪出張statement 囉, 無嫁啦"},{"pid":"33f09a749b1681bd540ea2a8e6dae3873a82e71e","tid":1626614,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c36da9664dc2f9de8242a0ad7388c95e70b6f213","tid":1626614,"uid":38960,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:13:43.000Z","msg":"封信真係無問題，就係咩人都盡力救<br />\n字眼嘅嘢，門面功夫嚟啫，始終都係政府部門"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:55:04.000Z","msg":"呢啲statement全部都係門面野 <br />\n從來都係睇啲人點執行<br />\n<br />\n差佬夠話自己serve with pride and care啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b32e8cc98482e92e8475a45a36a608cbd92c99","tid":1626614,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:55:14.000Z","msg":"831唔見你出聲?"}]}